      <text xml:space="preserve">{{pp-move-indef}}
{{About|the singer|her self-titled album|Aaliyah (album)}}
{{Use mdy dates|date=August 2010}}
{{Infobox musical artist &lt;!-- See Wikipedia:WikiProject Musicians --&gt;
