      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Refimprove|date=November 2009}}
{{Infobox Politician
| name            = Anton Drexler
| image           = 
| imagesize       =
| office          = [[National Socialist German Workers Party|Chairman of the DAP]]
| term_start      = 1919
| term_end        = 1921 
| predecessor     = [[Karl Harrer]]
| successor       = [[Adolf Hitler]]
| birth_date      = {{Birth date|1884|6|13|df=y}}
| birth_place     = [[Munich]], [[Germany]]
| death_date      = {{death date and age|1942|2|24|1884|6|13|df=y}}
| death_place     = [[Nazi Germany|Germany]]
| birthname       = 
| nationality     = [[Germany|German]]
| party           = [[National Socialist German Workers Party|DAP]]
