* {{Citation |ref=harv |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=JHgsfADZF9IC |title=Spelling and society: the culture and politics of orthography around the world |accessdate=2010-05-19 |first=Mark |last=Sebba |publisher=[[Cambridge University Press]] |year=2007}}
* {{Citation |ref=harv |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=I7qsTVO4IK4C |title=Language and national identity in Africa |accessdate=2010-05-31 |first=Andrew |last=Simpson |publisher=[[Oxford University Press]] |year=2008}}
* {{Citation |ref=harv |url=http://www.researchportal.be/en/project/mapping-linguistic-communication-across-colour-divides-black-afrikaans-in-central-south-africa-%28VUB_500000000019265%29/ |title=Mapping linguistic communication across colour divides: Black Afrikaans in Central South Africa |accessdate=2010-06-02 |first=Gerard |last=Stell |publisher=[[Vrije Universiteit Brussel]] |year=2008-11}} {{Dead link|date=September 2010|bot=H3llBot}}
* {{Citation |ref=harv |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=ujANkZqRALsC |first=Victor N. |last=Webb |year=2002 |title=Language in South Africa: the role of language in national transformation, reconstruction and development |work=Impact Studies in Language and Society |publisher=[[John Benjamins Publishing Company]]}}
* {{Citation |ref=harv |url=http://www.up.ac.za/academic/libarts/crpl/language-dev-in-SA.pdf |first=Victor N. |last=Webb |year=2003 |title=Language policy development in South Africa |work=Centre for Research in the Politics of Language |publisher=[[University of Pretoria]]}}
* {{Citation |ref=harv |url=http://www.grnnet.gov.na/aboutnam.html |title=Languages Spoken in Namibia |accessdate=2010-05-28 |year=2001 |last=Namibian Population Census |publisher=Government of Namibia}}
* {{Citation |ref=harv |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/wa.html#People |title=The World Factbook (CIA) — Namibia |last=CIA |year=2010 |accessdate=2010-05-28 |publisher=[[Central Intelligence Agency]]}}
